# Dynamic Theme Evolution System — Walkthrough

## Project Analysis Summary

### Architecture
| Aspect | Details |
|--------|---------|
| **Framework** | Next.js 16.2.4 (App Router), React 19.2.4 |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS v4 (`@tailwindcss/postcss`) + custom `@theme` tokens |
| **Fonts** | Inter (body), Space Grotesk (headings) via `next/font/google` |
| **Animations** | GSAP 3.15 + `@gsap/react`, Framer Motion 12.38, Lenis smooth scroll |
| **Other** | react-icons, react-hot-toast, typewriter-effect |

### Sections (8 total, in order)
1. **TopNavBar** — Sticky nav, glass backdrop, dropdown submenu, mobile hamburger
2. **HeroSection** — Profile image, typewriter roles, magnetic buttons, GSAP entrance
3. **AboutSection** — Bio, activities, stat cards (GSAP counter), GitHub stats
4. **SkillsSection** — SVG circular progress rings, marquee tech strip
5. **DetailedSkillsSection** — Skill groups with react-icons pills
6. **QualificationsSection** — Education/Experience timeline cards
7. **ProjectsSection** — 3D tilt project cards, filter tabs, modal trigger
8. **ContactSection** — Formspree contact form, contact info cards
9. **Footer** — Wave SVG, brand, quick links, social icons

### Design System
- **Primary accent**: Cyan `#00f0ff` (`--color-primary-container`)
- **Secondary accent**: Purple `#7000ff` (`--color-secondary-container`)
- **Tertiary accent**: Green `#00f6bb` (`--color-tertiary-container`)
- **Background**: Deep navy `#0b1326`
- **Glass cards**: `rgba(23,31,51,0.7)` with `blur(12px)` and cyan borders
- **Gradient text**: `from-cyan-400 to-purple-500`

---

## What Was Implemented

### Dynamic Theme Evolution System
A premium visual system that **auto-cycles through 4 distinct visual modes every 10 seconds** with smooth GSAP-powered color interpolation.

### Theme Modes

| Mode | Accent | Gradient | Feel |
|------|--------|----------|------|
| **Cyber Neon** (default) | Cyan `#00f0ff` | Cyan → Purple | Vibrant neon glows |
| **Glass Premium** | Violet `#a78bfa` | Violet → Blue | Frosted, softer feel |
| **Minimal Pro** | Slate `#e2e8f0` | White → Slate | Clean, professional |
| **Creative Motion** | Emerald `#34d399` | Emerald → Rose | Warm, expressive |

### What Changes Per Theme
- ✅ Background colors & surface tones
- ✅ Accent colors (buttons, borders, text highlights)
- ✅ Section title gradient colors
- ✅ Glass card backgrounds, borders & glow effects
- ✅ Ambient background radial gradients
- ✅ Skill ring / progress indicator colors
- ✅ Navigation active states & hover accents
- ✅ Back-to-top button color
- ✅ Footer link accents

---

## Files Changed

### [NEW] [ThemeEvolution.js](file:///d:/PROJECT/Next.js/My%20Portfolio/src/components/ThemeEvolution.js)
- Client component managing the 4-theme auto-cycle system
- Uses GSAP `gsap.to()` with a proxy object for smooth hex color interpolation
- Overrides Tailwind v4 CSS custom properties (`--color-*`) on `document.documentElement`
- Includes a compact theme indicator pill (bottom-left) with:
  - Current theme name & icon
  - Progress bar showing time until next cycle
  - Hover-to-expand theme selector popup
  - Pause-on-hover behavior

