---

## Architecture Decision: Why CSS Custom Properties + GSAP?

The key insight: **Tailwind CSS v4 compiles utilities to CSS custom properties**. For example, `text-cyan-400` resolves to `color: var(--color-cyan-400)`. By overriding these variables at runtime on `document.documentElement.style`, every Tailwind utility across all components automatically picks up the new colors — **zero component modifications required**.

GSAP handles the color interpolation natively (it detects hex strings and interpolates in RGB space), making transitions butter-smooth at 60fps.

## What Was NOT Changed
- ❌ No existing components were modified
- ❌ No existing animations were removed or altered
- ❌ No layout/responsiveness was affected
- ❌ No new dependencies were added
- ❌ No performance degradation (GSAP runs on requestAnimationFrame)

